task.summary: Adds enums for instrument type and colour.
Adds interfaces for IPlay, implmented in each InstrumentItem, and ISell, implementing at top-level Product, and sets the inheritance hieracrchy for all classes and subclasses.
Adds interfaces for IPlay, implmented in each InstrumentItem, and ISell, implementing at top-level Product, and sets the inheritance hieracrchy for all classes and subclasses.
Adds enums for instrument and item types, containing names, buying prices and in the case of the instrument an enum for instrument type.
Adds enums for instrument and item types, containing names, buying prices and in the case of the instrument an enum for instrument type.
Adds declarations and constructors for products, items, instruments and each individual instrument.

Adds in a new parent class called Component that takes in all of the instrument items so that they arraylist in instrument can now only take in this type of class. Adds tests for all getters created in Component/Instrument/Item.
Removes the InstrumentType Enum in favour of directly referencing the type in the InstrumentList enum instead.
Adds a sound String value to the component enum that is then passed in to the component constructor and uses a getter.
Adds Intrument methods and tests for getting the size of the components arraylist and for adding a component to it.
Adds component method and tests for Play (implemented interface method) and insturment method and tests for playInstrument.

Adds second playInstrument method that utilizes the IPlay interface. Removes the ISell interface in favour of inheritance. Adds shop class and test containing constructor, getter methods and tests and methods and tests for adding/removing and buying/selling products from the shop.
